cs.CR, cs.SI, cs.SE, cs.CY, cs.HC 

This paper focuses on privacy leaks in mobile operating systems and proposes a tool for detecting and measuring ongoing tracking across Android and iOS. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Other likely sub-categories include cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.SE (Software Engineering) as the paper discusses the development of a dynamic analysis tool. Additionally, cs.CY (Computers and Society) and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) are also possible sub-categories as the paper discusses the effectiveness of privacy safeguards and the impact on user privacy.
